{"tid":1648370,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"帶口罩係脫單秘訣","createTime":"2019-10-12T07:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T08:01:32.000Z","uid":329337,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1cc18b005c9edac4ec785cb1e58b3b3d975cd9","tid":1648370,"uid":329337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">帶口罩就會識到囡囡架！</span></span></strong><br />\n是咁的 今天我 收工果陣罷搭黨鐵 搭上了一架開往初戀既九巴 我上左上層之後坐左係車頭右邊靠窗位 坐定無幾耐 有一位黃衫少女亦都帶住口罩 走到黎車頭 左右兩邊望左一陣 決定揀同路人既我坐埋左一齊 我心諗幸福黎得真係太突然 機智既我當然唔會表露出內心飢渴 你知啦 香港人既精神就係無精神 巴士行左陣 我倆雙雙就聯機玩周公online  訓著左你知架啦 會愈坐愈近 幾乎頭碰頭 身為五十年不變A0表表者既我 差一點兒就把持不住 <br />\n開心既時間過得特別快 話咁快就到左屋企 我倆雙雙從周公online 番番黎香城online 好奇心驅使我偷偷瞄佢手機 佢同人wts緊 wallpaper係佢同一個男人既合照 而呢個男人 好肯定唔係佢老豆 完！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時化革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3fe2901996fb10320f6d45a8efd1cfd5b02dd365","tid":1648370,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa675ed18b588262eb9ca65c93888197a9f9da4","tid":1648370,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"自從戴左口罩<br />\nD人話我靚女左<br />\n下次試下戴埋眼罩<br />\n應該就似阿嬌"},{"pid":"35a65ed3bdb922d6b2371d3021c65ee4ba784135","tid":1648370,"uid":329337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa675ed18b588262eb9ca65c93888197a9f9da4","tid":1648370,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"自從戴左口罩<br />\nD人話我靚女左<br />\n下次試下戴埋眼罩<br />\n應該就似阿嬌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1